title: Harpon
description:
After a year full of trips, fun and events, Skating The Fish decided to make a film that covers most major skate sequences in Romania.
The film includes footage from cities like Bacau, Piatra Neamt, Buzau, Craiova, Bucharest, Drobeta-Turnu Severin, Ploiesti, Cluj-Napoca, Sibiu, Caracal, Slatina, Galati, Pitesti and Braila.
